    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロの事務所、雰囲気が明るくて活気があるわね",
      "startTime": 1.5999998649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "朝倉さんの逮捕騒ぎで一時は経営が危ぶまれましたが\nそこは業界最大手の芸能プロですから",
      "startTime": 10.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "協力者の援助もあって、今では経営も持ち直して\n日々勢いを増しているそうです",
      "startTime": 17,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "協力者の噂は私も聞いたことがあるわ\nバンプロを陰から支えたプロデューサーがいるって……",
      "startTime": 23.1426075619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "その人が持つ幅広い人脈と業界への影響力が\nバンプロを立て直す助けになったらしいわ",
      "startTime": 32.5092742285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "新人の育成に特に力を入れている方で\n今回遙子さんを講師に指名したのもその人みたいです",
      "startTime": 38.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "名前は聞いてませんが多くの人から愛され慕われている\n人物だそうです。……なんとなく遙子さんに似てますね",
      "startTime": 46.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "多くの人から愛され、慕われる人物……\nそういえば昔、三枝さんが言ってたわ",
      "startTime": 58.2702948255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "他者を想う優しさ、自分を諦めない強さ……\nそれらを貫いて頂点に立ったアイドルを俺は知っている",
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-shj002.m4a",
      "text": "両方を抱えたままアイドルとして成功出来れば\nキミも多くの人から愛され、慕われる存在になるだろう",
      "startTime": 79.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "VENUSプログラムが始まるよりも前に\n私と同じ想いを貫いて頂点に立ったアイドルがいた",
      "startTime": 89.284512965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "多くの人から愛され、慕われたアイドル……\n三枝さんが言ってたあの人が私を指名した人なのかしら",
      "startTime": 100.0548077904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYの裏で三枝さんと星見プロを助けて\n佐伯遙子というアイドルを見ていてくれた人……",
      "startTime": 111.1548077904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、遙子さん。バンプロの担当者さんが来ましたよ\nあれ？　一緒にいる女性は……",
      "startTime": 119.575751181,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 115.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、そうだったんですね\nお久しぶりです、星村さん",
      "startTime": 127.2568936988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――養成所での講義が始まって",
      "startTime": 130.623555144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "養成所に通うみなさん、初めまして\n私は星見プロ所属のアイドル。佐伯遙子、十七歳です",
      "startTime": 137.3235603654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "今日はアイドルにとって大事なことを\nみなさんに伝えに来ました",
      "startTime": 147.284512965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そうして遙子さんが後輩達に語ったのは）\n（自身のアイドル活動の軌跡だ）",
      "startTime": 152.6511796316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（辛い経験も恥ずかしい失敗も包み隠さず語る）\n（遙子さんは、俺にはとても格好良く見えて……）",
      "startTime": 158.3312671904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "これからあなた達は、何度も辛い経験をするでしょう\n悔しくて泣く日もあるかもしれない",
      "startTime": 167.9778684938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "誰かを羨むかもしれない。アイドルを辞めたいと\n思うかもしれない……。そんな時、思い出してほしいの",
      "startTime": 175.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "あなた達が憧れるアイドルの先輩達も\n同じ苦しみを乗り越えてきたことを",
      "startTime": 185.5778684938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "大事なのは、辛い時に自分を信じられるかどうか\n想いを貫けるかどうか",
      "startTime": 194.184512965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに大事なのは\n負けない心、挫けない心、諦めない心よ",
      "startTime": 199.3445392295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（以前、遙子さんから聞いたことがある）\n（負けない心、挫けない心、諦めない心……）",
      "startTime": 209.1511887868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（それは、遙子さんが尊敬する先輩……）\n（星村さんから伝えられて、受け継いだ言葉だ）",
      "startTime": 217.6000091552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
